    "body" : "<p>Try </p>\n\n<pre><code>SwingUtilities.updateComponentTreeUI(frame);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>If it still doesn't work then after completing the above step try</p>\n\n<pre><code>frame.invalidate();\nframe.validate();\nframe.repaint();\n</code></pre>\n"
