    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Here's some code that might help:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>&lt;yourJFrameName&gt; main = new &lt;yourJFrameName&gt;();    \nmain.setVisible(true);\nthis.dispose();\n</code></pre>\n<p>In this example, <code>main.setVisible(true);</code> will run the JFrame again, and <code>this.dispose();</code> will terminate the running window.</p>\n"
